import Vue from 'vue'
import App from './App'
import router from './router/'

import VueResource from 'vue-resource'
Vue.use(VueResource)

import VueRouter from 'vue-router'
Vue.use(VueRouter)

Vue.config.productionTip = false

new Vue({
  router,
  render: h => h(App)
}).$mount('#app')
